          <title>Ardour 9.0 released</title>
          <dc:creator><![CDATA[Paul Davis]]></dc:creator>
          <category>Blog</category>
          <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Ardour 9.0 is now available for Linux, macOS and Window systems. This is a major release for us, seeing several substantive new features that users have asked for over a long period of time. Region FX, clip recording, a touch-sensitive GUI, pianoroll windows, clip editing and more, not to mention dozens of bug fixes, new MIDI binding maps, improved GUI performance on macOS (for most) …</p>
<p><a href="https://ardour.org/download">Download</a> from the usual place, and read the full (rather long) <a href="https://ardour.org/whatsnew.html">release notes</a> …</p>
